{"title":"爱的明信片","authors":["峭岩"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":6,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱的明信片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从他们手里接过爱的火把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们再也不肯熄灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类从个体繁衍成一个星座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皆由于爱的永恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄去，我的心灵我的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你，夜以继日情里梦中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管阴雨雪雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都将你追踪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从有了爱的信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿就学会了凝望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望穿一轮红日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望成一群雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从母亲的襁褓里滑出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却滑不出爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即便是遥远的腾飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱依然跟踪未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许第一声歌啼并不嘹亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却是一支动情的恋歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许这一声唤来了知音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此结束了寂寞"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}